summary: An FBI Crisis Intake report dated July 8, 2019, documenting a call from a victim who reported being sexually abused by Jeffrey Epstein in 2004 when she was 14 years old in West Palm Beach, Florida. The report initiates a child sex trafficking investigation.

persons.name: Jeffrey Epstein

keyFacts: A victim contacted the FBI on July 8, 2019, to report being sexually abused by Jeffrey Epstein.
The abuse reportedly occurred in 2004 in West Palm Beach, Florida.
The victim was 14 years old at the time of the alleged abuse in 2004.
The FBI document classifies the matter as a 'CHILD SEX TRAFFICKING' investigation involving Jeffrey Epstein.
